column8: I guess I can help you!
Fee Fi Fo Fum, I can help you get it done!
Lulu always gets her work done. Mostly.
I'll do it after I play with Pix.
Oh, I love gifts. And surprises! And butterflies. What was I saying... Oh yeah, here's something for you!
Oh, you remembered I like gifts. And I remembered you like gifts. We all like gifts! Hopefully this one isn't as sticky.
Look at those fluffy ears... want to touch...
Look at those fluffy ears... want to touch...
Did you get that scar sticking your nose where it doesn't belong? Just kidding.
You're missing out on the river water though, for real.
Maybe I'm stronger than you. What do you think, Princey-poo?
Oh hi, I'm here, I'm here!
Your worst yordle nightmare is here to play!
Got here as fast as I could!
I'm here, I-- here I am!
Don't worry, Lulu will save you!
It's time for me to shine!
I'm the strongest spirit in any realm!
You got it, on the double!
I'll get right on it, Prince!
I really hate this part of the job, Miss Alune!
Miss Alune, I am so sorry!
Now break it up, you two!
I hate to see you fight!
Look at this big old wormy guy!
Oh wow that thing is huge!
Time to eat a big worm!
Oh wow this guy is huge!
Look at the size of this guy!
Would you look at this crowd?
Wow this place is amazing, Princey-poo!
It's Aphelios, what do you need me for?
Oh wow, it's that pretty boy!
Whoa is that Mother Moon's son?
Wait, the moon boy, that's him!
Ah, it's that scary old timer, Prince!!
I don't think I'm supposed to be here?!
Even Lulu doesn't want to get in trouble like this!
Something else I can do for you?
I guess I have some free time, Princey-poo.
Want a tulip? No? I guess I can still help you.
You give worm-heads a bad name!
Get ready for the real deal, worm heads!
You girlies won't know what hit you!
Come get a taste of purple medicine!
Worm-heads causing problems for you, Princey-poo?
Let's see if she likes purple--Yikes! Eek!
Hey, girlie, let's see what you've got!
Oh wow, look at you go!
Wow, would you look at that!
Never look a tulip in the eye.
Good thing we have this bond!
He really does have a LOT of spills...
I knew you could do it!
All right, this place is clean! C-L-E-A-N!!!
Don't mess with my pet dog!!
I do have lots of fans!
No Karthus, you cannot pet my doggy!
Oopsies... we left Karthus with some bumpy-wumpies...
Um, no hard feelings, right creepy skull face?
